entry.tran: 有自我约束力的;能律己的
entry.def: Someone who is self-disciplined has the ability to control themselves and to make themselves work hard or behave in a particular way without needing anyone else to tell them what to do.

example.ex: Most religions teach you to be truthful and self-disciplined.
example.tran: 多数宗教教导人们要真诚和律己。
